summary: This cable discusses Joachim Joesten, a writer with possible ties to communist organizations and anti-KUBARK sentiments. It requests a thorough check of his background, writings, and possible connections, including his fiancee Anna Schinsky. The matter is of interest to the Warren Commission.
title: KIGREST TRACES JOACHIM JOESTER
recipient: BONN, FRANKFURT, BERLIN, COPENHAGEN, REYKJAVIK, PARIS, STOCKHOLM DIRECTOR THE HAGUE BRUSSELS
